{"type":"message","id":"0f0efbe8","parentId":"f409977d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T16:29:25.540Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-20 00:29 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索道简网络相关行业最新动态：\n1. 企业数字化转型最新政策/趋势\n2. 智能安防行业最新动态\n3. 网络系统集成/信创最新消息\n4. IT运维/AIOps最新进展\n\n搜索关键词：企业数字化转型 智能安防 网络系统集成 IT运维 AIOps 2026年3月\n\n请返回3-5条最新的关键信息，每条包含：标题、核心要点、对道简网络的启示"}],"timestamp":1773937765538}}
{"type":"message","id":"9d763f9f","parentId":"0f0efbe8","timestamp":"2026-03-19T16:29:33.617Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我作为子代理，搜索道简网络相关行业的最新动态。需要搜索4个方向：\n1. 企业数字化转型最新政策/趋势\n2. 智能安防行业最新动态\n3. 网络系统集成/信创最新消息\n4. IT运维/AIOps最新进展\n\n关键词：企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维、AIOps、2026年3月\n\n我需要使用web-search技能来进行搜索。让我先读取这个技能的文档。","thinkingSignature":"e2ba79c1a7c4385c29f767dd97c9d046801acc791c5fca7cc449bfe9535ea812"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rfhku1rda000_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":117,"output":139,"cacheRead":18914,"cacheWrite":11892,"totalTokens":31062,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0001668,"cacheRead":0.0005674199999999999,"cacheWrite":0.0014270399999999999,"total":0.0021963599999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773937765539}}
{"type":"message","id":"6ba22393","parentId":"9d763f9f","timestamp":"2026-03-19T16:29:33.627Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_rfhku1rda000_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773937773624}}
{"type":"message","id":"4396189b","parentId":"6ba22393","timestamp":"2026-03-19T16:29:38.434Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我需要使用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 命令来搜索相关信息。让我搜索这4个方向的最新动态。\n\n我需要进行多次搜索：\n1. 企业数字化转型 2026年3月 政策\n2. 智能安防 2026年3月 行业动态\n3. 网络系统集成 信创 2026年3月\n4. IT运维 AIOps 2026年3月 进展\n\n让我并行执行这些搜索。","thinkingSignature":"101cbfd052406bac6b22466a791bb540aea64e306fa007234c2c4c4a450e4825"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2ujv0zm0c7q9_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026年3月 政策趋势\" --output json","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2ujv0zm0c7q9_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 2026年3月 行业动态\" --output json","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2ujv0zm0c7q9_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 信创 2026年3月\" --output json","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2ujv0zm0c7q9_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维 AIOps 2026年3月 进展\" --output json","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":929,"output":319,"cacheRead":30648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31896,"cost":{"input":0.0002787,"output":0.0003828,"cacheRead":0.0009194399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0015809399999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773937773626}}
